    • Method Detail

      • dataChanged

        void dataChanged(JvmstatModel jvmstat)
        Invoked when counters are updated. This event is generated at a fixed interval as determined by the polling rate of the JvmstatModel that the JvmstatListener is registered with.
        Parameters:
        jvmstat - the JvmstatModel that this listener is registered with.
